 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢d 地方一定無可能有下文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好冇下文啦 2舊水 60分鐘 咁都有下文就抵我出埋火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f7434edb84d22246644418498d3ca57db1b406","tid":58652,"uid":59705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"邊度有靚女正骨,扯恆條j比佢睇都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91175c60d1707103d1ce5cf2ddb0f2e3f1f73c3a","tid":58652,"uid":51851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"全程扯住係一份尊重, 何必咁介懷"},{"pid":"45c399bb2fd297dad03b6cc54c100fdfae10bd53","tid":58652,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度有靚女正骨,扯恆條j比佢睇都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n度度都有啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab72d87a6b17c562deae48652d7385149d5d622","tid":58652,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全程扯住係一份尊重, 何必咁介懷</blockquote><br />\n咁我都好欽敬啲技師"}]}